PoliticInfo - Class in com.service.politic13
Manage all the politicians that clients can add We get back to client all the informations about the politicians with this class All the information : the age, the politicla party We manage all the politicians in HashMap with a string for the key that is politician name, and for the value the PoliticInfo's instance
PoliticInfo() - Constructor for class com.service.politic13.PoliticInfo
Constructor to call and create an instance of this class in PoliticUser class to get the informations from the hash map

Another constructor to create an instance whith age, political party and Twitter name in parameter in the hash map in the method managePolitic() Returns the following status code : 'name' is added : succesfully added
politicInList(String) - Method in class com.service.politic13.PoliticUser
Detect if a politician is in client's politician list Returns the following status code : true : the politician is in the list false : the politician is not in the list This method is called when the client wants to get Information about one his politicians list
PoliticUser - Class in com.service.politic13
The class whith Jax-ws annotations that will be called by the client In this class we manage the client's politician list, all the information that will be retrieved by the client We call for that 2 class : TwitterManage, PoliticInfo We retrieve API Twitter request from the class TwitterManage
